{"tid":1672076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗暴之戰】今生只嫁前線巴 勇武絲剖白：唔好彩俾人告暴動要坐十年 我會等佢","createTime":"2019-10-24T01:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T19:27:27.000Z","uid":77355,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7f8da5281caeef206786817a0d33b4d6385bc2","tid":1672076,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191024/60160552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60160552&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoSfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=90d59317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60160552&h=b23a13eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191024/60160552</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢咁唔好彩俾人告暴動要坐十年，我會等佢。」<br />\n「我都會。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】養和醫院稱社會運動致病人減少 為財政穩健暫停招聘<br />\n<br />\n訪問前在餐廳吃飯，在臉上略施脂粉，穿着短裙的兔兔依偎着石內卜，邊餵食邊輕聲耳語。被閃光彈照個正着的記者看得出，眼前一對二十出頭的年輕人正處於熱戀期。「佢有時都會有公主病，會嗲吓我咁，其實我哋都係一對好普通嘅情侶。」但只要換上一襲黑衣，兩人便雙雙變成「火魔法師」，一同走上戰場最前線，與防暴和速龍埋身肉搏。<br />\n<br />\n這對抗爭運動生成的情侶，每一次聯手出動，都是性命和未來的一場賭注。亂世中的愛，或許脆弱，卻也堅貞。「我之前同佢講過，如果佢咁唔好彩俾人告暴動要坐十年，我會等佢。」「我都會。」看着身軀略為顫抖的兔兔，石內卜想也不想，許下承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連條女都勇過人"},{"pid":"0f1a5f569df0eaff6626bcd6356ee2f05535d299","tid":1672076,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"火魔師但係埋身肉搏？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/voc58C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h